            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-732c1b25-0538-48dc-9df3-f04fb32b6f86">
                Wing-Commander Wright
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-732c1b25-0538-48dc-9df3-f04fb32b6f86" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
