<p class="">I thought the right hon. Gentleman was going to make a correction of the statement in the Press.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-142ea4c3-b0b3-49ac-81a1-2022c4e5d2e9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
