<p class="">There is a great deal of talk about some statement in the Press. Are we not entitled to know what the statement was, so that we may know what the right hon. Gentleman and the hon. and gallant Gentleman are talking about?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
