<p class="">Considering the many, many months my Noble Friend and I struggled to galvanise the present Government, I think that a little hard.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f9f173b2-f506-469f-8f20-3b9635dd9712" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
