        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-dd5cea2e-ea2a-44e0-a46a-0d0c4f0cb81f'>
            
<p class=""><em>It being after Eleven of the Clock and objection being taken to further Proceed</em><span id="1880" class="column-number" data-column-number="1880"></span> <em>ing,</em> THE CHAIRMAN <em>left the Chair to make his Report to the House.</em></p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div>

